sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as Operator Controller<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant Kustomize as Kustomize Engine<br/>In-Process
    participant LlamaStack as Llama Stack Pod<br/>8321/TCP
    participant Ollama as Ollama Server<br/>11434/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>ServiceMonitor

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 1: LlamaStackDistribution Creation
    User->>K8sAPI: Create LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>Auth: kubeconfig credentials
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch notification (In-Process)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Get LlamaStackDistribution<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>Kustomize: Render manifests from templates
    Kustomize-->>Controller: Rendered YAML
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment, Service, PVC<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR Created

    Note over User,LlamaStack: Flow 2: ConfigMap Update and Pod Restart
    User->>K8sAPI: Update llama-stack-operator-config<br/>Auth: kubeconfig credentials
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch notification (ConfigMap changed)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Deployment pod template<br/>Add/Update annotations
    K8sAPI->>LlamaStack: Rolling restart (new pods)

    Note over User,vLLM: Flow 3: Llama Stack Inference Request
    User->>LlamaStack: POST /v1/models/inference<br/>8321/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Optional TLS 1.3
    LlamaStack->>Ollama: Inference request<br/>11434/TCP HTTP
    Ollama-->>LlamaStack: Inference result
    LlamaStack-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over LlamaStack,vLLM: Alternative: vLLM Inference
    LlamaStack->>vLLM: Inference request<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Optional Token Auth
    vLLM->>HF: Download model (first run)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: HF Token
    HF-->>vLLM: Model artifacts
    vLLM-->>LlamaStack: Inference result

    Note over Controller,Prometheus: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Token Review<br/>Validate ServiceAccount
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Token valid
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics<br/>reconcile_total, errors, duration
